PLACEHOLDER - not a real PE image.

This is the slot where the NT kernel image will go once it is built. The
loader's PE-load + handoff path (M3) will read it from here. For now it is a
stand-in so the OS directory has a kernel-sized file to list. Replace it by
having the kernel build write its output to loader/ramdisk/root/OS/NTOSKRNL.EXE.
